Lindsay, who was marrying Chris Williams, 28, said it meant a lot to have her father's blessing.

'I kind of thought that I would've 
been looking at Chris when I was walking down the aisle with Augie, but I
 couldn't look at anything but my dad,' Lindsay, 25, told TODAY.com.

'I was just amazed he was able to get in his device and stand up. The sun was in his eyes, and I was just thinking that he's done so much to be here and worked so hard that I just started bawling,' she added.

